text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\"><img alt=\"7毫米超纤薄 希捷单碟500GB本盘评测\" src=\"http://2a.zol-img.com.cn/product/93_500x2000/554/cedQFS2yq4Bo.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\n<b>希捷Momentus Thin 单碟500GB笔记本硬盘的厚度</b></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 希捷Momentus Thin 单碟500GB笔记本硬盘的盘体厚度仅7毫米，实测大约6.9毫米。它采用单张500GB碟片结构，因此在提升硬盘容量和性能的同时，也能保持超纤薄的厚度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 该硬盘采用G-Force Protection技术，非常适合那些对耐用性要求极高的移动用户甚至狂热发烧友用户。G-Force Protection能够增强硬盘运行时的抗冲击能力，能够承受1000 Gs的非工作状态抗震能力和350 Gs的工作状态抗震能力，从而更有效地保护数据。</span></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(194,217,242) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 4px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); margin-top: 20px; text-indent: 0px; padding-left: 5px; font: 14px/21px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><span style=\"float: right\">产品：<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\">Momentus Thin 500GB 5400转 16MB（ST500LT012）</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\">希捷</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\">硬盘</a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\" name=\"p3090246\"><img alt=\"回到顶部阅读\" align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://icon.zol.com.cn/doc/2010/top.png\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" /></a></span></span></span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">希捷单碟500GB本盘的盘体识别</span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">我们通过软件识别希捷Momentus Thin 单碟<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">500GB</a><a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">笔记本硬盘</a>的盘体。其型号为ST500LT012，接口为SATAII 3Gbps速率，转速为5400RPM，缓存为16MB，总使用时间为O。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img alt=\"爱不释手 希捷极致轻薄移动硬盘首测\" src=\"http://2e.zol-img.com.cn/product/91_500x2000/556/ce3E7wBqK6fhU.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"617\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /><br />\r\n<b>CDM软件识别希捷Momentus Thin 单碟500GB<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">笔记本硬盘</a></b></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(194,217,242) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 4px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); margin-top: 20px; text-indent: 0px; padding-left: 5px; font: 14px/21px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><span style=\"float: right\">产品：<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\">Momentus Thin 500GB 5400转 16MB（ST500LT012）</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\">希捷</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\">硬盘</a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\" name=\"p3090247\"><img alt=\"回到顶部阅读\" align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://icon.zol.com.cn/doc/2010/top.png\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" /></a></span></span></span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">HD Tune测试：平均读取超80MB/秒</span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">● ATTO Disk Benchmark</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">ATTO Disk Benchmark是一款优秀且免费的磁盘基准测试软件，支持对稳定性/突发性传输速率进行读写测试，适用于常规<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">硬盘</a>、RAID、USB闪存盘、移动存储卡等<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">产品</a>的读写性能测试。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img alt=\"7毫米超纤薄 希捷单碟500GB本盘评测\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/93/559/cebEOZh6v5Ls.jpg\" width=\"482\" height=\"576\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">队列深度4时 最大读写速度测试</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">提示：</strong>相信很多网友都会遇到这样的问题，就是硬盘产品在出厂标称中的读取和写入速度都比自己测试的数值大，其实厂商就是通过ATTO Benchmark和CrystalDiskMark软件测试得出的最大数值。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">在ATTO Benchmark速度测试中，希捷Momentus Thin 单碟<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">500GB</a><a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">笔记本硬盘</a>的读取速度达到104.4MB/秒；其写入速度达到106.3MB/秒。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr style=\"border-bottom: 1px inset; border-left: 1px inset; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; height: 1px; color: gray; border-top: 1px inset; border-right: 1px inset; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">● CrystalDiskMark</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">CrystalDiskMark是一款简单易用的硬盘性能测试软件，但测试项目非常全面，涵盖连续读写、512K和4KB数据包随机读写性能，以及队列深度（Queue Depth）为32的情况下的4K随机性能。队列深度描述的是硬盘能够同时激活的最大IO值，队列深度越大，实际性能也会越高</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\"><img alt=\"7毫米超纤薄 希捷单碟500GB本盘评测\" src=\"http://2a.zol-img.com.cn/product/93/560/ceekSdVgLhco.jpg\" width=\"406\" height=\"368\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">CrystalDiskMark测试</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">从CrystalDiskMark测试看，希捷Momentus Thin 单碟500GB<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">笔记本硬盘</a>的读取速度达到103.6MB/秒，而写入速度也达到103.2MB/秒。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 小结：</strong>综合两项权威测试软件所得出的结果，该款本盘的最大读写速度和平均读写速度可圈可点，希捷的首款7毫米单碟500GB<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">笔记本</a>硬盘较之老款双碟500GB/5400转，它在性能上有明显提升，接近普通7200转本盘的性能。</span></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(194,217,242) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 4px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); margin-top: 20px; text-indent: 0px; padding-left: 5px; font: 14px/21px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><span style=\"float: right\">产品：<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\">Momentus Thin 500GB 5400转 16MB（ST500LT012）</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\">希捷</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\">硬盘</a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\" name=\"p3090249\"><img alt=\"回到顶部阅读\" align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://icon.zol.com.cn/doc/2010/top.png\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" /></a></span></span></span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">HD Tach：突发读取超200MB/秒</span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">● 底层测试：HD Tach</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">HD Tach读速度测试不依赖于文件系统，曲线成绩基本相当于<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">硬盘</a>内部传输速率测试。体现的是很理想化的硬盘速度，其外延部分大约是磁盘性能表中buffer to disk项目的反映，而真实应用中，极少有机会达到这样的高度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img alt=\"7毫米超纤薄 希捷单碟500GB本盘评测\" src=\"http://2c.zol-img.com.cn/product/93_500x2000/562/ceV2evpKkdmCM.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"366\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">希捷Momentus Thin500GB<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">笔记本硬盘</a>的HD Tach平均读取性能测试</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在HD Tach速度测试中，希捷Momentus Thin 单碟<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">500GB</a><a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">笔记本硬盘</a>的平均读取速度达到84.3MB/秒，几乎达到3.5吋<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">台式机</a>5400转节能硬盘的速度。其突发读取速度达到惊人的218.9MB/秒，接近入门级<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">固态硬盘</a>的速度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: simhei\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 本盘拥有如此出色的突发读取速度，基于它作为新一代<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">产品</a>的异类，和其他品牌7毫米单碟500GB本盘的<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">8MB缓存</a>相比，它是较为少见配备<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">16MB缓存</a>的同类产品，因此更能发挥和延长突发读取速度的持续时间，对整体性能有一定提升。</span></span></p>','images/201306/thumb_img/1709_thumb_G_1372233107557.jpg','images/201306/goods_img/1709_G_1372233107523.jpg','images/201306/source_img/1709_G_1372233107531.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1367274444','100','0','0','0','0','0','